        {
            "body": "Hmm. The reason I like schema is they provide an easy way to know what the json should look like, not just checking whether it works.\r\nI think the fact that some stuff might be hard to express with json schema is probably an indication that the schema we would be using is too complex.\r\nWhat kind of thing would schema not be flexible enough for ?\r\n(it would be possible to provide sub-schema for each datatype btw)",
